high_descs: Walk to the toilet.
Grab the toilet paper roll on the floor between the toilet and the wall.
Turn around, walk to the shelf on the right.
Place the toilet paper roll on the black and brown shelf.
Turn to the left, walk to the white drawers with the brown top.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper on behind the spray bottle.
Turn to the right, walk back to the shelves to the right of the bathtub.
Place the toilet paper next to the toilet paper roll on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the toilet paper with the toilet paper roll on the shelf by the bathtub.

high_descs: Turn left then head towards the toilet.
Remove the toilet paper roll from the roll holder.
Turn all the way around then head towards the tall white cabinet
Place the toilet roll on the bottom shelf.
Turn all the way around then head towards the door, then right towards the cabinet next to the sink.
Pick up the full roll of toilet paper behind the spray bottle from the cabinet.
Turn all the way around head towards the toilet, turn left then head towards the tall white cabinet.
Place the full toilet paper roll to the left of the empty roll on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a full roll and an empty roll of toilet paper on the bottom shelf of the tall white cabinet.

high_descs: Walk forward to the right side of the toilet.
Grab the empty toilet paper roll off of the floor.
Turn around and walk to the shelves.
Place the empty roll on the lower shelf.
Turn right and walk to the counter nearest the door.
Grab the toilet paper.
Head back to the shelves behind.
Place the toilet paper next to the empty roll.
anns.task_desc: Place toilet paper and an empty roll on the shelf.
